---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Team - Experten für Laborcontainer" description="Das Planexus Team: Sven Biewald und Thomas Boss - Experten für Laborcontainer und Modulbau mit über 10 Jahren Erfahrung." canonical="/team">
  <div class="pt-20 min-h-screen bg-white">
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?q=80&w=2070')] bg-cover bg-center opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 via-slate-900/95 to-slate-900"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">Das Planexus Team</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Erfahrung trifft Innovation. Wir sind Ihre Experten für Laborbau.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden group shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-bl-full -mr-8 -mt-8 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150 duration-700"></div>
            <img src="/team/sven-biewald.jpg" alt="Sven Biewald" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover object-top mb-6 shadow-md" />
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">Sven Biewald</h3>
            <p class="text-primary font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Gesellschafter / Visionär</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Der Pionier der modernen Laborcontainer. Mit über einem Jahrzehnt Erfahrung und einem unbändigen Willen zur Innovation treibt er die Vision von Planexus voran.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sven-biewald-893a85a3/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors text-slate-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sven.biewald.90" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors text-slate-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden group shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-bl-full -mr-8 -mt-8 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150 duration-700"></div>
            <img src="/team/thomas-boss.jpg" alt="Thomas Boss" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover object-top mb-6 shadow-md" />
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">Thomas Boss</h3>
            <p class="text-primary font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Gesellschafter / Technik</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Der technische Kopf hinter den Kulissen. Seine Expertise garantiert, dass visionäre Ideen in funktionale, robuste Realität umgesetzt werden.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-boss-690091352" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors text-slate-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/thomas.boss.9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors text-slate-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 border-t border-gray-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-center mb-16 text-slate-900">Was unsere Kunden sagen</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-primary/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 italic relative z-10 leading-relaxed">"Die Zusammenarbeit bei der Planung unseres neuen Labors war hervorragend. Von der ersten Konzeptidee bis zur finalen Umsetzung wurden all unsere Anforderungen berücksichtigt."</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Dr. Martina Weber</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium">Laborleiterin</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-primary/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 italic relative z-10 leading-relaxed">"Planexus hat für unser Forschungszentrum ein innovatives technisches Konzept entwickelt, das sowohl effizient als auch zukunftssicher ist."</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Prof. Dr. Thomas Keller</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium">Forschungsleiter</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-primary/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 italic relative z-10 leading-relaxed">"Dank der kompetenten Vertriebsbegleitung durch Planexus konnten wir unsere technischen Produkte gezielt am Markt platzieren."</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Susanne Lehmann</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium">Vertriebsleiterin</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
